Also it is hard to guage my health and my pets at the same time in my HP bar. <br>
<br>
Suggestions: can you make the pet bar part of our stamina bar instead?  Do other party members see our pets health in our hp bar?  Or perhaps change the yellow to another color? Or do it as a thin bar like the blue bar in our exp?<br>
<br>
Either way it is FANTASTIC having my pets hp visible. Thank you.<br>
<br>
All in all its a pretty nice interface and allows quite a few options.<br>
